---
title: Roasted Chicken & Gravy Supper with Carrots, Garlic-Herb Mashed Potatoes & Green Beans
description: Nothing says comfort food like classic homestyle roasted chicken with gravy. You'll rub a half-chicken with garlic-herb butter, then roast over a bed of carrots and onion. Serve with garlic-herb mashed potatoes, tender green beans, and velvety gravy for a timeless Sunday roast-style meal that's perfect any night of the week.
